Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs28\fad(150,100)}制作 十六夜 ？ 秋月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fade(100,100)}与宿命之战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚安之目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎样才能成王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉基亚的卡梅隆提督啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个都城的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太乏味了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议负责人正在找斯卡卢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败战处理这种会议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么新发展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之把蒙古鲁今后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托给库穆和尤拉尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我在下面等您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就要回阿鲁古斯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在看不到地平线的地方我会闷死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不待在海上就平静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢沿海州的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备去诺斯弗拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺斯弗拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在布拉多大公的隐藏房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了某些资料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面这样写着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺斯弗拉斯的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡著称霸世界的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 诺斯弗拉斯才正是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万物发祥之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是解开世上谜团的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你为了证实才...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信什么兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么万物发祥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想那里潜藏着与众不同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是据说没有一个人能活着走出诺斯弗拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是有人去挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫卡路·莫露的魔道士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡路·莫露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过斯卡卢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说这些给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题问得无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且我要说给谁听这是我来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这件事绝不能让纳利斯知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能从诺斯弗拉斯活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时请一定来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢回阿鲁古斯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他说要先行一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢要去诺斯弗拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要去那种不毛之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡梅隆提督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天斯卡卢闷在布拉多大公的隐藏房间很久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有阿慕涅莉丝远征诺斯弗拉斯的资料不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连斯卡卢大人都被你派人监视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果认为我纳利斯是友人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你认同我是友人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请相信我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想与斯卡卢为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说的我真不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天就回帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快点回巴拉基亚为好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡梅隆提督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久疏问候 塔里奥大公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对自己今后的生活有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体恐怕已经不属于我自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说库穆要如何处理我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请容我这样问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的长子塔露从托拉斯回来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参考尤拉尼亚的意向再裁决你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你年轻美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受审处决也太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你愿意我也可以助你重建蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以库穆为后台重建蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蒙古鲁要全权委任给库穆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是成为库穆的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留下蒙古鲁之名只有这个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡既是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦完成了任务就可以轻松地暗杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被新主人取代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还不如接受裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以死向帕罗的民众道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我这样说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被俘之身还要想要威胁我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蒙古鲁公主阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么 您变得高大起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你是忠实的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库穆就满足于背后操纵蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话请说您出心中所有的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蒙古鲁的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且殿下您膝下还有三位没娶妻的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 答案就只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事等塔露回来再和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前公主大人说变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到会那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是库穆的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却可以那么挺胸抬头地说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想他所想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺水推舟而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所说的他是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库里斯塔鲁公爵 阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是无可代替的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿慕涅莉丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库穆的二王子塔露·赞殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和三王子塔里库殿下想见您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人同时？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先请塔露·赞进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了一个可疑之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是来求救的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当我被盗贼袭击时救我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人长着匪夷所思的豹头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说豹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来是那个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在那个洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部队在这待命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看身后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真费劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不被直觉敏锐的你察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是刺客之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有兴趣的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只许帕罗圣王权才能操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代机械
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才来见你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶之诗想要进入我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你纯洁的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你染黑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要进入我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利亚多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是迦南帝国的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦南帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三千年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配中原和奇塔伊、诺斯弗拉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的第一大帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦南所有的钟开始共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被从天而降的陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致这场灾难的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你 奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奎因？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因才是这个世上恶之根源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶之魂的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 奎因不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明降临到你们身上的灾难都是奎因带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆斯不要相信他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们会被指引到露德之森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后一直遇险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是奎因唤来的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说也许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你说这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只说我是恶之根源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿不出别的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你对我一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你对自己有所了解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少了解一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沿着自己相信的路走到今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且今后也会走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你这种人出场的份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定要灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落入暗黑世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿库拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道阿库拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然伤害到我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的本来面目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因 让你见识一下你也战胜不了的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白费劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和迦南的墓碑一起消散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利亚多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在诺斯弗拉斯也出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向北
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向北 就能明白我的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白我的命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你跑了 奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜塔尔族库大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时在岛上看到的光球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过去 琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要救奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是诺斯弗拉斯的荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺斯弗拉斯怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达和雷姆斯在诺斯弗拉斯的荒野徘徊过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 在想这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 能看到库里斯塔鲁的宫殿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达 雷姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿慕涅莉丝去过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是斯卡卢想要去的诺斯弗拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里肯定有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我也必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光球在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像梦中见到的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利亚多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来死期还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因 奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去编制出的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环绕悠久时间的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编织众神的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却不了激动的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.15,0:24:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这就是开始的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.45,0:24:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 起程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.63,0:24:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚安的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
